  <li>
    <p><span class="spoiler">
Use the instructions to shift the letter found in the previous step. So first line
A:ALPHA (BACKWARDS) = ‚ÄúSEMAPHORE SHIFT SIX‚Äù = C (Semaphore was side
C) +6 = 9 = I
</span></p>
